Keywords: Amiga Guide to ALL big Scene Parties
Requires: about 1Mb ChipMem
Version:  3/97  (3 of 3 in 1997, rel. 04-Nov-97)


THE SCENE GUIDE - LIFE IS A PARTY!


WHAT IS IT?

  "The Scene Guide" (current issue is 3 of 3 in 1997)
  is a fat AMIGA GUIDE ABOUT *ALL BIG* AMIGA PARTIES,
  presenting the  results of the competitions of each
  party and new party invitations, with very detailed
  information about each production.

NUMBERS OF THIS ISSUE:

  - more than 1300 Kb of plain ascii-text !!!
  - 307 parties!
  - 2267 productions !
  - 2 pictures
  - 2 modules

WHAT`S NEW?

  What`s new in this issue? - Added 331 productions
  and 43 parties;  completed many  entries with the 
  help of  Skull/Eremation and  Skid/Ozone - thanks
  dudes!; included lsasg search funtion; many, many
  reviews and opinions added and other cool things!

